      "content": "It sounds like you are deeply convinced that your absence would bring peace to everyone around you, and that feeling of being a burden is incredibly heavy. But what you are describing is a permanent solution to temporary, exhausting feelings, and that is a dangerous kind of logic. If you are feeling this desperate, please know that there are people who want to listen without judgment. You can connect with the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline by calling or texting 988 anytime.",
      "source": "target",
